Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.98,0:00:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.99,0:00:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.10,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.31,0:00:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.39,0:01:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.14,0:01:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.21,0:01:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民衛星派來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.22,0:01:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五部鋼彈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.35,0:01:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是衛星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈躲藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開聯合軍機動戰士部隊的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以OZ為攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開了各種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.07,0:01:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ終於踏上歷史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.97,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,統帥特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以精銳的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.28,0:01:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行了消滅聯合軍的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派來地球的機動戰士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.95,0:02:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的戰鬥令大地震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由這裡開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有親人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為自己所犯的錯誤接受審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.30,0:02:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙想做的事好徹底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真卑鄙!竟然想讓我這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你自己得到解脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有這種生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.48,0:02:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五話\N[前往決戰地點南極]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最後一個，死心了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要道歉也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.67,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然殺死和平論者不可饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是被OZ巧妙地騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也並非不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己的生死交由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己殺死的人的家屬處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若繼續做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.84,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人發現只是時間的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去收拾他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那身體別勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運送這東西不能用陸路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用船嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.38,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，被那班人嚴密監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也很困難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如用我的運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你真的還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是第一次這樣和你們見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是路克蕾琪亞‧諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是傑克斯特校的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在西伯利亞和你交手的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可束手就擒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校說想見你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想見我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳以為能從我們身上\N問出情報嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非以OZ軍人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是以機動戰士駕駛員的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想見你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想再次和你們戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想決鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫傑克斯的是個出色的男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信不信由你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你信他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙不像會設陷阱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的機動戰士會有幫助啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西伯利亞基地自爆了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈駕駛員的生死還未能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我想聯絡\N和那部鋼彈交手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ駕駛員傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他已經離開維多利亞基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未能取得聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是甚麼也不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，有一件事是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.78,0:06:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校的行動\N有可疑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校在西伯利亞一戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.18,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從宇宙運來大量鋼彈特殊合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.96,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是用來修理回收的鋼彈吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那被OZ的當權派知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被毀滅的事，我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，有情報說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈其實是仿製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仿製品!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運來的鋼彈特殊合金的數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來足以製成兩部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一部的數量用來製造仿製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘下的就用來修理嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他究竟為何\N那麼執著於鋼彈呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想決一高下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,13年前，他6歲時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.80,0:07:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾經做他練劍的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.76,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個不喜歡佔對手便宜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識傑克斯特校嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他曾是匹斯克拉福特的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多英勇事蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.94,0:07:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，若能聯絡上傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會知道希洛的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有一個人在找希洛‧唯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是諾邊塔夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是在新愛德華\N被妳認識的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死的聯合最高司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔元帥的遺孀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那看來也是OZ不知道的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你馬上聯絡諾邊塔夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還活著吧!諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他的生命力強得驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也覺得對不起妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是要妳做些多餘的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是機動戰士的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點了解傑克斯你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝妳，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要格外小心調查隊的跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾，我們不能派人支援妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳們自己要設法瞞過他們耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01有最終調整一定要趕得及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校炸毀的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是仿製品的傳聞正在擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以再讓傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續自做主張嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團裡也有很多問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由維多利亞開始跟蹤的調查隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是會令我添麻煩的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都太擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是OZ的運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?他們或許在裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,袖手旁觀可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別急，他們一定會露出尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前繼續監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.51,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再讓他們為所欲為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.92,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左手重量的平衡有自動控制嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我刻意沒裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了令接近戰更敏捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的身體已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們和普通年輕人毫無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果現在殺死他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就不用\N傑克斯特校冒險吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還未明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.82,0:11:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做會被傑克斯討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.93,0:11:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盾也裝在機關砲的手臂上嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，若是平時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會想讓別人碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你那樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就快點記熟它的特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.71,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今次一定會\N打倒那傢伙給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聯絡上諾邊塔夫人後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她寄來了這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她希望借莉莉娜小姐的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它送到收信人手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔夫人寄來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是給希洛‧唯先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給希洛的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的突然來訪令我吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當時不能把心中所想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦白告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.36,0:12:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我寫了這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要停止責備自己在戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.97,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰上所犯的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些純真的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想快點創造能快樂生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然諾邊塔死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也會為過去所犯的\N錯誤而痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你們還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們想著創造未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一族能和你們見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實感光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望無戰爭的世界盡快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給親愛的希洛‧唯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還活著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上去西西里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和諾邊塔夫人\N見面打聽希洛所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我馬上準備飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.89,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛果然還活著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可讓重要的客人著涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿上它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們飛向哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在冰雪覆蓋的大陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行機動戰士戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.22,0:14:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為\N不在那種地方會惹人注目啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,須要測試能力的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經全部修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可只是能測試的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想修理到和原來一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?為何要那樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這部機動戰士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛它的駕駛員的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.34,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N不可能完全修好它的右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,揮動巨大激光炮的力量和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,揮舞光劍的系統的修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.12,0:14:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,須要制造一部\N新機動戰士的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少用托爾吉斯左手的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成01光劍的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.63,0:15:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校\N你究竟想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.87,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒天真的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家，來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在發出修理01右手的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵特尉!不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被數部調查隊的運輸機跟著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.55,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一進入大陸就出現反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們計算這部機的續航距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.83,0:15:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們認為我們會逃進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校所在的基地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們改變方向擾亂他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，只要放下兩部艾亞利玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能甩掉追兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地的位置被知道也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候就迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.68,0:15:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不會告訴他們\N傑克斯的所在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳用艾亞利玆出擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳只會被敵人擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你們平安送到基地\N是我的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我照自己意思做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩部艾亞利玆自由落下中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有識別訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要被拙劣的戲騙到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.55,0:16:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進攻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.79,0:16:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1號機中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人2號機再被擊中就會爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別急!暫時躲進雲裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!我要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起!我真大意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望兩位帶我們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯和鋼彈那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我掩護妳!諾茵特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我們去救諾茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你違反命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格批評我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急速掉頭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好天真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了!我們投降!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戰鬥也沒用!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們拋掉武器了，我們投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳以為背叛了羅姆斐拉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會用得上那規則嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果交出鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,証明傑克斯叛變就另當別論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.36,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，即使那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯的命運都會一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會在南極這裡殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以功勞來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊倒他會被認為有更大的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以\N讓你們見到傑克斯!!
